PEiD(suggested)
Download PEiF tool ->https://softfamous.com/peid/ 
Execute PEiD tool 
Upload malware executable 
See entry point address

PEView 
Download PEView tool 
Execute tool 
Upload malware executable 
Look for the "Optional Header" section within the PEView interface. In this section, 
you should find the "AddressOfEntryPoint" field, which represents the entry point of the executable. 
Note the hexadecimal value displayed in the "AddressOfEntryPoint" field. This is the entry point address of the executable.

